3. To-Do List
A simple to-do list application that allows users to manage their daily tasks. The app includes:
Add Tasks: Users can add tasks with descriptions.
Mark as Complete: Users can mark tasks as completed.
Delete Tasks: Users can remove tasks from the list.
HTML: Structure of the list
CSS: Styling and layout
JavaScript: Task management logic
